### Create an application version

POST http://localhost:3000/applications/{{application_id}}/versions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "version": "1.1.0",
  "changelog": "Added another cool new feature!"
}


### List all applications versions

GET http://localhost:3000/applications/{{application_id}}/versions HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get application version details

GET http://localhost:3000/applications/{{application_id}}/versions/{{version_id}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update application

PUT http://localhost:3000/applications/{{application_id}}/versions/{{version_id}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "changelog": "Fixing a typo in my changelog"
}

### Delete application

DELETE http://localhost:3000/applications/{{application_id}}/versions/{{version_id}} HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
